    <h2 id="cta-heading" class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
      ¿Listo para transformar tu práctica legal?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Déjanos tu nombre y correo para enviarte una invitación al Preview gratuito.
    </p>
    <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      Al lanzar la versión completa, los pioneros accederán al plan profesional con tarifa preferencial.
    </p>

    <!-- Invitation Request Form -->
    <div class="max-w-md mx-auto">
      <%= form_with url: "#", method: :post, class: "space-y-4", data: { turbo: false } do |f| %>
        <div>
          <label for="full_name" class="sr-only">Nombre completo</label>
          <input
            type="text"
            name="full_name"
            id="full_name"
            placeholder="Nombre completo"
            required
            class="w-full px-5 py-4 bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-xl text-white placeholder-white/60 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/50 focus:border-transparent transition-all duration-200"
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="email" class="sr-only">Correo electrónico</label>
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            id="email"
            placeholder="tucorreo@ejemplo.com"
            required
            class="w-full px-5 py-4 bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-xl text-white placeholder-white/60 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/50 focus:border-transparent transition-all duration-200"
          >
        </div>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="w-full px-8 py-4 text-primary-700 font-semibold bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 shadow-elevation-2 hover:shadow-elevation-3 hover:-translate-y-0.5 flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
